data.description: This beautiful home is located in the most greatly desired neighborhood in La Hoya Texas.  A spacious modern home with a modern farmhouse design situated on over an acre of land. The exterior features light gray siding and black trim with large windows overlooking the private backyard. A three-car garage is attached to the home. Interior details include an open floor plan with high ceilings, porcelain floors, a gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, and a master suite with a walk-in closet and luxury bath. Total living area is over 2,500 square feet.
